We can connect to databases from different data sources like excel, JSON, and many more.


Step 1: connection to the database : Select whatever datasource you want to work with in this case we are using excel
Step 2: After importing the dataset into Tableau  : Then select sheet from left bottom corner and import datasource into sheet
Step 3: Importing data source into the workbook : Dataset has been imported left sides we are can see all the columns just to see how it works i had clicked the 
                                                   prod_category column to see the total order ( it's kind of seeing total order value by every product category)
